import React from "react";
import Box from "@mui/material/Box";
import Sidebar from "../components/Sidebar";
import Topbar from "../components/Topbar";
import StatCard from "../components/StatCard";
import ActionCard from "../components/ActionCard";
import Grid from "@mui/material/Grid";
import Typography from "@mui/material/Typography";
import Button from "@mui/material/Button";
import CloudUploadIcon from "@mui/icons-material/CloudUpload";

function Dashboard({ mode, setMode }) {
  return (
    <Box sx={{ display: "flex" }}>
      <Sidebar />
      <Box sx={{ flexGrow: 1 }}>
        <Topbar mode={mode} setMode={setMode} />
        <Box sx={{ p: 3 }}>
          <Typography variant="h4" fontWeight={700}>Dashboard Overview</Typography>
          <Typography variant="body1" mb={2} color="text.secondary">
            Railway operations management at a glance
          </Typography>
          {/* STAT CARDS */}
          <Grid container spacing={2} mb={2}>
            <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
              <StatCard label="Trains Ready" value="147" sublabel="180" icon="train" positive />
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
              <StatCard label="Maintenance Alerts" value="8" sublabel="Active" icon="build" />
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
              <StatCard label="Ad Deadlines" value="3" sublabel="This Week" icon="timer" />
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
              <StatCard label="System Health" value="98.2%" sublabel="Uptime" icon="check_circle" positive />
            </Grid>
          </Grid>
          <Box display="flex" justifyContent="flex-end" mb={2}>
            <Button variant="contained" color="primary" startIcon={<CloudUploadIcon />}>Input Upload</Button>
          </Box>
          <Typography variant="h6" fontWeight={700} mt={2} mb={1}>Quick Actions</Typography>
          <Grid container spacing={2} mb={2}>
            <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
              <ActionCard label="Data Prediction" description="View operational analytics" icon="show_chart" />
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
              <ActionCard label="Maintenance Hub" description="Job cards and fitness tracking" icon="build_circle" />
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
              <ActionCard label="Train Audit" description="Detailed train profiles" icon="account_box" />
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
              <ActionCard label="Stabling Status" description="Bay allocation overview" icon="place" />
            </Grid>
          </Grid>
          {/* Add more sections below as needed */}
        </Box>
      </Box>
    </Box>
  );
}

export default Dashboard;
